在一张图表中</h2><p>以下是需要避免的最常见的投资错误，从情绪驱动的投资到支付过多的费用。 </p></div><!--mvp-blog-story-text--></div><!--mvp-blog-story-in--></div><!--mvp-blog-story-out--></li><li class="mvp-blog-story-wrap left relative infinite-post"><div class="mvp-blog-story-out relative"><div class="mvp-blog-story-img left relative"><img loading="lazy" width="400" height="240" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/OC_BlackRocks-Equity-Holdings_Shareable-400x240.jpg" class="mvp-reg-img lazy wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/OC_BlackRocks-Equity-Holdings_Shareable-400x240.jpg 400w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/OC_BlackRocks-Equity-Holdings_Shareable-1000x600.jpg 1000w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/OC_BlackRocks-Equity-Holdings_Shareable-590x354.jpg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /><img loading="lazy" width="80" height="80" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/OC_BlackRocks-Equity-Holdings_Shareable-80x80.jpg" class="mvp-mob-img lazy wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/OC_BlackRocks-Equity-Holdings_Shareable-80x80.jpg 80w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/OC_BlackRocks-Equity-Holdings_Shareable-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/OC_BlackRocks-Equity-Holdings_Shareable-100x100.jpg 100w" sizes="(max-width: 80px) 100vw, 80px" /></div><!--mvp-blog-story-img--><div class="mvp-blog-story-in"><div class="mvp-blog-story-text left relative"><div class="mvp-cat-date-wrap left relative"><span class="mvp-cd-cat left relative">股票</span><span class="mvp-cd-date left relative">9个月前</span></div><!--mvp-cat-date-wrap-->贝莱德顶级股权可视化</h2><p>贝莱德是全球最大的资产管理公司，持有超过 9 万亿美元的资产。以下是该公司持有的主要股权。 </p></div><!--mvp-blog-story-text--></div><!--mvp-blog-story-in--></div><!--mvp-blog-story-out--></li>