按国家可视化天然气储量https://www.visualcapitalist.com/cp/visualizing-natural-gas-reserves-by-country/ https://www.visualcapitalist.com/cp/visualizing-natural-gas-reserves-by-country/#respondBruno Venditti Mon, 04 Mar 2024 19:24:01 +0000 Energynatural gasFuelRussialngliquified natural gasBPFossil fuel https://www.visualcapitalist.com/?post_type=cp&p=164729 <p>俄罗斯的储量最多，占全球总量的20%左右。</p><p><a href="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/cp/visualizing-natural-gas-reserves-by-country/">各国天然气储量可视化</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.visualcapitalist.com">Visual Capitalist</a>上。</p> ; <div class="rss-image"><p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Natural-Gas-Reserve-Sep-16-2023-Compressed-1.jpg" alt="按国家/地区显示已探明天然气储量的堆积条形图。"></p></div><h2>按国家可视化天然气储量</h2><p>天然气用于发电、为房屋和建筑物供暖以及为车辆提供动力。它也是各种工业过程中的原材料。</p><p>在这张图中，创建者 Gopalakrishnan Ravichandran 按国家对天然气储量进行了排名。他使用的数据来自<a href="https://www.bp.com/en/global/corporate/energy-economics/statistical-review-of-world-energy.html#tab_sr-2021" target="_blank" rel="noopener">bp Statistical Review</a> ，截至 2023 年 9 月。</p><h2>俄罗斯拥有最大的储备</h2><p>天然气、煤炭和石油是数百万年来随着植物和动物遗骸与沉积物混合并承受压力和热量而形成的。</p><p>天然气储层是地下区域，其中天然气被困在多孔且可渗透的岩层中，并受到不透水岩石或水屏障的限制。</p><p>探明储量是指在现有经济和运营条件下可采收的天然气量。当成功钻探新的探井时，这些储量可能会<a href="https://www.eia.gov/energyexplained/natural-gas/how-much-gas-is-left.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">增加</a>。</p><p>俄罗斯的储量最大，为37.4万亿立方米，约占全球总量的20%。伊朗位居第二，占总储量的 17%，其次是卡塔尔，占 13%。 </p><p><table id="tablepress-3978" class="tablepress tablepress-id-3978"><thead><tr class="row-1 odd"><th class="column-1">国家</th><th class="column-2">储备（中医）</th><th class="column-3">百分比</th></tr></thead><tbody class="row-hover"><tr class="row-2 even"><td class="column-1"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1f7-1f1fa.png" alt="🇷🇺" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />俄罗斯联邦</td><td class="column-2">37.4</td><td class="column-3"> 19.9% </td></tr><tr class="row-3 odd"><td class="column-1"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1ee-1f1f7.png" alt="🇮🇷" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />伊朗</td><td class="column-2">32.1</td><td class="column-3"> 17.1% </td></tr><tr class="row-4 even"><td class="column-1"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1f6-1f1e6.png" alt="🇶🇦" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />卡塔尔</td><td class="column-2">24.7</td><td class="column-3"> 13.1% </td></tr><tr class="row-5 odd"><td class="column-1"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1f9-1f1f2.png" alt="🇹🇲" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />土库曼斯坦</td><td class="column-2">13.6</td><td class="column-3"> 7.2% </td></tr><tr class="row-6 even"><td class="column-1"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1fa-1f1f8.png" alt="🇺🇸" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />我们</td><td class="column-2">12.6</td><td class="column-3"> 6.7% </td></tr><tr class="row-7 odd"><td class="column-1"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1e8-1f1f3.png" alt="🇨🇳" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />中国</td><td class="column-2">8.4</td><td class="column-3"> 4.5% </td></tr><tr class="row-8 even"><td class="column-1"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1fb-1f1ea.png" alt="🇻🇪" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />委内瑞拉</td><td class="column-2">6.3</td><td class="column-3"> 3.3% </td></tr><tr class="row-9 odd"><td class="column-1"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1f8-1f1e6.png" alt="🇸🇦" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />沙特阿拉伯</td><td class="column-2">6.0</td><td class="column-3"> 3.2% </td></tr><tr class="row-10 even"><td class="column-1"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1e6-1f1ea.png" alt="🇦🇪" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />阿拉伯联合酋长国</td><td class="column-2">5.9</td><td class="column-3"> 3.1% </td></tr><tr class="row-11 odd"><td class="column-1"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1f3-1f1ec.png" alt="🇳🇬" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />尼日利亚</td><td class="column-2">5.5</td><td class="column-3"> 2.9% </td></tr><tr class="row-12 even"><td class="column-1"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1ee-1f1f6.png" alt="🇮🇶" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />伊拉克</td><td class="column-2">3.5</td><td class="column-3"> 1.9% </td></tr><tr class="row-13 odd"><td class="column-1"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1e6-1f1ff.png" alt="🇦🇿" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />阿塞拜疆</td><td class="column-2">2.5</td><td class="column-3"> 1.3% </td></tr><tr class="row-14 even"><td class="column-1"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1e8-1f1e6.png" alt="🇨🇦" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />加拿大</td><td class="column-2">2.4</td><td class="column-3"> 1.3% </td></tr><tr class="row-15 odd"><td class="column-1"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1e6-1f1fa.png" alt="🇦🇺" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />澳大利亚</td><td class="column-2">2.4</td><td class="column-3"> 1.3% </td></tr><tr class="row-16 even"><td class="column-1"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1f0-1f1ff.png" alt="🇰🇿" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />哈萨克斯坦</td><td class="column-2">2.3</td><td class="column-3"> 1.2% </td></tr><tr class="row-17 odd"><td class="column-1"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1e9-1f1ff.png" alt="🇩🇿" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />阿尔及利亚</td><td class="column-2">2.3</td><td class="column-3"> 1.2% </td></tr><tr class="row-18 even"><td class="column-1"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1ea-1f1ec.png" alt="🇪🇬" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />埃及</td><td class="column-2">2.1</td><td class="column-3"> 1.1%</td></tr><tr class="row-19 odd"><td class="column-1">其他的</td><td class="column-2">18.1</td><td class="column-3"> 9.6%</td></tr><tr class="row-20 even"><td class="column-1">全部的</td><td class="column-2">188.1</td><td class="column-3"> 100.0%</td></tr></tbody></table><!-- #tablepress-3978 from cache --></p><p>按地区划分，亚洲在储量方面占据主导地位，有 6 个国家跻身前 10 名。同时，非洲、欧洲、北美和南美各有 1 个代表。</p><p>尽管美国的探明储量排名第五，但它是最大的天然气<a href="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/which-countries-produce-the-most-natural-gas/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">生产国</a>，占全球份额的 23%。俄罗斯位居第二（17.4%），伊朗位居第三（6.4%）。</p><p>此外，美国还是主要的天然气出口国，2022年通过管道出口天然气827亿立方米，液化天然气(LNG)出口1043亿立方米。俄罗斯是全球第二大天然气出口国，其次是卡塔尔和挪威。</p><p><a href="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/cp/visualizing-natural-gas-reserves-by-country/">各国天然气储量可视化</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.visualcapitalist.com">Visual Capitalist</a>上。</p> ; https://www.visualcapitalist.com/cp/visualizing-natural-gas-reserves-by-country/feed/ 0 164729
